highlights.text: Ronnie Flex has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Hoe Het Is” is the highest at #2.
“Hier Mag Alles” by Donnie and Marco Schuitmaker has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 604 days straight.
“Rather Be (feat. Jess Glynne)” by Clean Bandit and Jess Glynne is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 60 spots at #134.
